Class ModuleVersion

    • org.azyva.dragom.model.ModuleVersion

  • public final class ModuleVersion
extends Object
    Represents a specific Version of a Module. Includes a NodePath (which cannot not be partial) and a Version.

    Implements value semantics. Instances are immutable.

    Implements hashCode() and equals(java.lang.Object) so that instances can be used as Map keys.

    ModuleVersion support the literal form <NodePath>:<Version> where <NodePath> is the NodePath in String format and <Version> is the Version in literal form.

    Example: Acme/module:D/master
